Not cheering at all!

84
00:10:12,654 --> 00:10:14,195
Take that! And that!

85
00:10:14,524 --> 00:10:15,637
And that!

86
00:10:16,227 --> 00:10:19,308
They weren't cheering!
They weren't cheering me!

87
00:10:24,816 --> 00:10:26,170
Those crooks!

88
